OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780391237
OL,3,CThousands in Kent still facing water
OL,4,Csupply issues
OL,6,FThousands of people in Kent are still
OL,7,Ffacing water supply issues as the
OL,8,Fcounty enters its tenth day of
OL,9,Fdisruption.
OL,11,FMore than 100 households in Mereworth,
OL,12,Fa village near Maidstone, currently
OL,13,Fhave no water.
OL,15,FSouth East Water says more than 3,000
OL,16,Fcustomers may experience low pressure
OL,17,For an intermittent supply during the
OL,18,Fday in the Coxheath, Loose, Headcorn,
OL,19,FUlcombe, Benenden and Kemsing areas.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
