PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780391237
OL,3,CThousands in Kent still facing water
OL,4,Csupply issues
OL,6,FThe problems began during the recent
OL,7,Fheatwave, affecting properties in Kent
OL,8,Fand Sussex, and people are being asked
OL,9,Fto use water for essential purposes
OL,10,Fonly.
OL,12,FLast week, residents in Whistable were
OL,13,Fleft washing and brushing their teeth
OL,14,Fin the sea and yesterday a care home
OL,15,Fin Cranbrook was forced to clean
OL,16,Fresidents with wet wipes after days
OL,17,Fwithout water.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
