OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780391237
OL,3,CThousands in Kent still facing water
OL,4,Csupply issues
OL,6,FIn a statement, South East Water's
OL,7,FIncident Manager, Mike Court, said:
OL,8,F"Drinking water supplies are
OL,9,Fcontinuing to return to customers
OL,10,Facross Kent today.
OL,12,F"Currently there are around 117
OL,13,Fhouseholds with no water in the
OL,14,FMereworth area due to low levels in
OL,15,Four drinking water storage tank which
OL,16,Fsupplies the area, however we expect
OL,17,Fsupplies to be restored today.
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780391237
OL,3,CThousands in Kent still facing water
OL,4,Csupply issues
OL,6,F"Although our network is continuing to
OL,7,Frecover, levels of drinking water in
OL,8,Four storage tanks across Kent are
OL,9,Fstill low and we are asking customers
OL,10,Fto use water for essential purposes
OL,11,Fonly - drinking, cooking, and hygiene.
OL,12,FWe are continuing to use our tankers
OL,13,Fto support the network and aid
OL,14,Frecovery.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780391237
OL,3,CThousands in Kent still facing water
OL,4,Csupply issues
OL,6,F"There are 3,164 customers who may
OL,7,Fexperience low pressure or an
OL,8,Fintermittent supply during the day in
OL,9,Fthe Coxheath, Loose, Headcorn,
OL,10,FUlcombe, Benenden and Kemsing areas.
OL,11,FThis means that water will go on and
OL,12,Foff throughout the day, with no water
OL,13,For low pressure at peak times,
OL,14,Fparticularly between 7am to 9am and
OL,15,F4pm to 7pm.
OL,17,F"We are sincerely sorry to customers
OL,18,Ffor disruption to their water supply
OL,19,Fand know how frustrating it is,
OL,20,Fespecially in hot weather.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780391237
OL,3,CThousands in Kent still facing water
OL,4,Csupply issues
OL,6,F"We are doing everything we can to get
OL,7,Ftreated water into our drinking water
OL,8,Fstorage tanks, including using our
OL,9,Ftankers to support the network and
OL,10,Fensuring all available treatment works
OL,11,Fare running at full capacity.
OL,13,F"We have been delivering water to
OL,14,Fschools in affected areas this morning
OL,15,Fto ensure they can open as planned.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780391237
OL,3,CThousands in Kent still facing water
OL,4,Csupply issues
OL,6,F"In areas where there has been a
OL,7,Fsupply interruption - or where we
OL,8,Fbelieve issues may continue to occur -
OL,9,Fwe're delivering bottled water to
OL,10,Fcustomers on our Priority Services
OL,11,FRegister.
OL,13,F"We have delivered more than half a
OL,14,Fmillion bottles of water to customers
OL,15,Fon our Priority Services Register and
OL,16,Falso delivered bottled water to
OL,17,Fcritical care settings such as care
OL,18,Fhomes, GP surgeries, pharmacies and
OL,19,Fdentists.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
