OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780391237
OL,3,CThousands in Kent still facing water
OL,4,Csupply issues
OL,6,F"We have been working 24/7 with our
OL,7,Ffleet of tankers to support our
OL,8,Fnetwork where demand has been
OL,9,Fextremely high. So far, we have
OL,10,Ftankered over 2,627,912 litres of
OL,11,Fwater into the network.
OL,13,F"We have also given out over one
OL,14,Fmillion litres of water at our bottled
OL,15,Fwater stations across Kent.
OL,17,F"Additionally, we are supporting the
OL,18,FQueen Victoria Memorial Hospital in
OL,19,FHerne Bay and an urgent care unit with
OL,20,Fa tanker and supporting those with
OL,21,Flivestock.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780391237
OL,3,CThousands in Kent still facing water
OL,4,Csupply issues
OL,6,F"Although the weather has cooled, we
OL,7,Fare continuing to ask customers in
OL,8,Fsupply to use water for essential
OL,9,Fpurposes only - for example drinking,
OL,10,Fcooking and hygiene.
OL,12,F"Customers can find FAQs, details of
OL,13,Fbottled water stations and information
OL,14,Fabout locations currently experiencing
OL,15,Fsupply issues via our website.
OL,17,F"For updates, please visit
OL,18,Faqualerter.southeastwater.co.uk".
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOUzD@`O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
